Banner Table View 

Installation:

- Add the source code files to your project under its own directory
  
Usage:

  - Initialize using BannerTableViewController class
  Example:
  
  BannerTableViewController *banners = [[[BannerTableViewController alloc] init] autorelease];
  
  - Save banner data when application moves to inactive state, usually in 
  applicationDidEnterBackground and applicationWillTerminate
  
  [bannerTableController archiveData];
  
Configuring:
  
  - See Settings.h for configurable values
  - To modify the UI, see BannerTableCell.xib

